wo podnosi\u0107 ceny.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Dzi\u0119ki tym krokom mo\u017cesz lepiej zrozumie\u0107 rynek i dostosowa\u0107 swoj\u0105 strategi\u0119 cenow\u0105, co przyniesie korzy\u015bci Twojej marce.<\/p>\n<p>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak analizowa\u0107 strategie cenowe konkurencji w bran\u017cy Beauty i FMCG?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy kiedykolwiek zasta<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4069,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4068","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4068"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4068"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4068\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4069"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4068"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4068"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4068"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}